It was a [[Baloch people|Baloch]] nationalist guerrilla group,<ref name="crisisbalochistan.com">http://www.crisisbalochistan.com/secondary_menu/writers/karlos-zurutuza/baloch-from-afghanistan-between-insurgency-and-famine.html</ref><ref name="balochvoice.com">http://www.balochvoice.com/News/English/2001/01-11-24_Baloch_Provinces_of_Afghanistan_Seek_Independence.html</ref> representing the [[Baloch people]] of southwestern Afghanistan.

