'''''Případ nevěrné Kláry''''' ("The Case of Unfaithful Klara") is a [[Czech language|Czech]] novel, written by [[Michal Viewegh]]. It was first published in 2003.<ref name="Czech Lit">{{cite web |title=Michal Viewegh |url=http://www.czechlit.cz/en/author/michal-viewegh-en/ |website=Czech Lit |accessdate=27 July 2018}}</ref>

The book was made into [[The Case of Unfaithful Klara (film)|a film of the same name]] in 2009.

